{"id":80643,"date":[{"year":1946,"month":1,"day":7}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"世纪风","column":"","genre":"","count":"184","ytitle":"","mtitle":"冬及其他","ftitle":"","authors":["臧克家"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战争里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八个年头风雪的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在流亡中磨过去了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年，胜利后的第一个冬天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜最长，也最寒冷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声“最后胜利”的消息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡顿然离我遥远了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利把他们留住了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天望着飞机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天上飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天听到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长途汽车的啦叭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和轮船启碇的鸣叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有办法的“真牌”难民，(注)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却被胜利留在山南海北了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注:腰缠百万的人凭“难民证”买票上船，而无钱无力的真正难民却被留下了!)"}]}